messages.ssml: <speak>According to the World Health Organization, the “incubation period” is the time between catching the virus and showing symptoms of the disease. Most estimates of the incubation period for <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> range from 1-14 days, most commonly around five days. These estimates will be updated as more data becomes available.</speak>
